Advanced 3+ Years IAM Questions
21. What are SCPs in AWS Organizations?

SCP (Service Control Policy) organization level pe maximum permissions define karti hai.

Even admin user bhi SCP restrictions bypass nahi kar sakta.

22. What are Permission Boundaries?

Maximum permissions limit define karti hain for IAM users/roles.

Delegated administration me useful.

23. Explain policy evaluation logic.

AWS evaluate karta hai:

SCP
Permission boundaries
Session policies
Identity policies
Resource policies

Final decision:

Explicit deny → deny
Allow required from applicable policies
24. Difference between AWS managed and Customer managed policies?

AWS Managed:

AWS maintain karta hai

Customer Managed:

Hum create/manage karte hain
More customization
